description:
OCEAN UNDERWATER ATTACK!

Winter is coming, and it's gonna be a long and cold one, so as a proud shark you need to get your food reserve as high as possible before winter comes. So eat as much as sea horses and fishes while avoiding sea mines and scuba diver.

Get as far as you can in the ocean, the journey will be dangerous be with enough strength you should be able to get through winter, it's coming soon so you're a bit in a rush, after all it's an emergency ! Humans are infesting the water trying to find treasures, they've put underwater mines for their protection, you'll have to navigate carefully not to be blown up !

DOWNLOAD SHARK WINTER EMERGENCY for FREE now!
